  "detailed_description": "<h1>Chuck's biggest concern!</h1><p>One day Chuck’s wife gets kidnapped by a pterodactyl much to Chuck’s delight. He’s pretty happy at first but eventually gets hungry and quickly comes to appreciate his wife’s cooking skills. He sets out to free his woman.<br><br>In Caveman Chuck you’re taken back all the way to the Stone Age where you play the role of a crude caveman named Chuck. You’ll quickly realize he shares his cave with his wife, who is heavily invested in the relationship, and as things often have it, she yells at him rather frequently.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Caveman Chuck is a classic 2D platformer inspired by the many favorites of the genre. You are taking a control over a caveman named Chuck who is fearless prehistoric warrior who.. lost his wife.. He need to overcome plains full of dangerous animals and traps, challenge even more dangerous bosses to bring her back home!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922650/extras/f9c566fe03e234b426edce9296345359.poster.avif?t=1671022071\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922650/extras/f9c566fe03e234b426edce9296345359.webm?t=1671022071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922650/extras/f9c566fe03e234b426edce9296345359.mp4?t=1671022071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Prehistoric bosses brings unique platformer-based experience! Challenge them to find Chuck's wife!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922650/extras/b289458a641c8cfb7bd04e1464ded345.poster.avif?t=1671022071\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922650/extras/b289458a641c8cfb7bd04e1464ded345.webm?t=1671022071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922650/extras/b289458a641c8cfb7bd04e1464ded345.mp4?t=1671022071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Start Chuck's journey and travel across sunny deserts, frozen wilds, dangerous jungles, and plains!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922650/extras/1bde1995c8832cf1c264e7dc9ed1811b.poster.avif?t=1671022071\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922650/extras/1bde1995c8832cf1c264e7dc9ed1811b.webm?t=1671022071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922650/extras/1bde1995c8832cf1c264e7dc9ed1811b.mp4?t=1671022071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Enhance Chuck's power with bones found in-game!<br><br>",
